0&quot;}" data-image-title="vtuber_agency_noripro_makes_major_announcements_including_1st_audition" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vtuber_agency_noripro_makes_major_announcements_including_1st_audition.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vtuber_agency_noripro_makes_major_announcements_including_1st_audition.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" src="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/vtuber_agency_noripro_makes_major_announcements_including_1st_audition.jpg?resize=1100%2C619&#038;ssl=1" alt="VTuber办公室Nori Pro发布重要公告，包括首次举行试镜" class="wp-image-100132" data-recalc-dims="1"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">佃纪男 图片来源： <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lw6OCs_rkPY" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="YouTube">YouTube</a><br> © 诺里临</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>Nori Pro于11月20日宣布，旗下艺人白雪三白郎、爱宫弥留、姫咲结弦、猫濑野真将于12月底毕业，并于2024年1月（令和6）起成为个人艺人。执行为</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="w9uQ6oU7kj"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/noripro-4-vtubers-graduated-at-the-end-of-december/">Nori Pro 的 VTuber“Mishiro Shirayuki”、“Milk Aimiya”、“Yuzuru Himesaki”和“Shin Nekoseno”毕业并转向个人活动。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Nori Pro VTuber“Mishiro Shirayuki”、“Milk Aimiya”、“Yuzuru Himesaki”和“Shin Nekoseno”毕业并转向个人活动” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/noripro-4-vtubers-graduated-at-the-end-of-december/embed/#?secret=eFCLlIqqfX#?secret=w9uQ6oU7kj" data-secret="w9uQ6oU7kj" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>此外，当天，白雪三代郎、爱宫弥留、姫咲结弦、猫濑野真根据Nori Pro的官方公告进行了分发。虽然他明确表示并不是因为对经纪公司不满而辞职，但由于合同关系，他无法透露原因，所以一些观众和粉丝可能会想， <em>“其实他是在良好的条件下毕业的。”</em> 「<em>难道不是这样吗？」</em>以及「<em>我没有听到任何人才对佃谷纪夫表示感谢。」</em>看来确实如此。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="AOHzzLXXvq"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/streaming-by-4-vtubers-shirayuki-mishiro-enomiya-milk-himesaki-yuzuru-and-nekozeno-shin-who-will-graduate-from-noripro/">Nori Pro 毕业 VTubers Mishiro Shirayuki、Miruku Aimiya、Yuzuru Himesaki 和 Shin Nekoseno 即将播出</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Nori Pro 毕业 VTubers Mishiro Shirayuki、Miruku Aimiya、Yuzuru Himesaki 和 Shin Nekoseno 将进行直播” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/streaming-by-4-vtubers-shirayuki-mishiro-enomiya-milk-himesaki-yuzuru-and-nekozeno-shin-who-will-graduate-from-noripro/embed/#?secret=NzVglHzdOa#?secret=AOHzzLXXvq" data-secret="AOHzzLXXvq" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><div class="vdatv6560fd23ce3e1" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
